<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
    <style>
/* Reset default browser styles */
* {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    box-sizing: border-box;
}

/* General body styling */
body {
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    line-height: 1.6;
    background-color: #f4f4f9;
    color: #333;
    padding: 20px;
}

/* Header styling */
header {
    background: #007bff;
    color: white;
    padding: 10px 0;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
}

header h1 {
    font-size: 24px;
}

/* Main content styling */
main {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    background: white;
    padding: 20px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
}

/* Table styling */
table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    margin-top: 20px;
}

table th,
table td {
    border: 1px solid #ddd;
    padding: 8px;
    text-align: left;
}

table th {
    background-color: #007bff;
    color: white;
}

table tr:nth-child(even) {
    background-color: #f9f9f9;
}

table tr:hover {
    background-color: #f1f1f1;
}

/* Form styling */
form {
    margin-top: 20px;
    padding: 20px;
    background: white;
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
}

form label {
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 5px;
    font-weight: bold;
    color: #333;
}

form input,
form select,
form textarea {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    border: 1px solid #ccc;
    border-radius: 4px;
    box-sizing: border-box;
}

form button {
    background-color: #007bff;
    color: white;
    padding: 10px 15px;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 4px;
    cursor: pointer;
    text-decoration: none;
}

form button:hover {
    background-color: #0056b3;
}

/* Link styling */
a {
    color: #007bff;
    text-decoration: none;
    margin-right: 5px;
}

a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
}

/* Button styling for actions */
.action-button {
    background-color: #007bff;
    color: white;
    padding: 10px 15px;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 4px;
    cursor: pointer;
    text-decoration: none;
    margin-right: 5px;
    display: inline-block; /* Ensure links are displayed as buttons */
}

.action-button:hover {
    background-color: #0056b3;
}

/* Button styling for delete */
.delete-button {
    background-color: #dc3545;
    color: white;
    padding: 10px 15px;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 4px;
    cursor: pointer;
    text-decoration: none;
    margin-right: 5px;
    display: inline-block; /* Ensure links are displayed as buttons */
}

.delete-button:hover {
    background-color: #c82333;
}

/* Styling for index page */
.index-page {
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 20px;
}

.index-page h2 {
    font-size: 24px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    color: #333;
}

.index-page p {
    font-size: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    color: #666;
}

.index-page ul {
    list-style-type: none;
    padding: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 10px; /* Spacing between buttons */
}

.index-page ul li {
    margin: 0; /* Remove margin from list items */
}

.index-page ul li a {
    background-color: #007bff;
    color: white;
    padding: 10px 20px;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 4px;
    cursor: pointer;
    text-decoration: none;
    display: inline-block;
    width: 100%; /* Full width buttons */
    box-sizing: border-box; /* Include padding and border in width */
}

.index-page ul li a:hover {
    background-color: #0056b3;
}

.index-page ul li a:hover {
    background-color: #0056b3;
}
    </style>
</head>
<body>
</header>
<main>
    <div class="index-page">
        <h2>Selamat Datang di Sistem Manajemen Rumah Sakit</h2>
        <p>Ini adalah halaman utama aplikasi.</p>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="/pegawai" class="action-button">Kelola Pegawai</a></li>
            <li><a href="/dokter" class="action-button">Kelola Dokter</a></li>
            <li><a href="/poli" class="action-button">Kelola Poli</a></li>
            <li><a href="/pasien" class="action-button">Kelola Pasien</a></li>
            <li><a href="/antri" class="action-button">Kelola Antrian</a></li>
            <li><a href="/reservasi" class="action-button">Kelola Reservasi</a></li>
            <li><a href="/pembayaran" class="action-button">Kelola Pembayaran</a></li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</main>
</body>
</html>
